{
  "stem": "1581.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he managed to befriend a German soldier, not an SS man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well I found, when I-- after liberation, we had some gentile friends in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they gave me a bundle of letters they received through these soldiers, from my brother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in this letter, he described what was going on with him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And his last letter was dated in August of 1943.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if you want to, I would like to read--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to you--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--What this letter said.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While he was in Minsk, his wife suffered from a perforated ulcer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they tried to operate on her on a kitchen table, and she died.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was really desolate about this loss.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he managed to stay alive 'til '43.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In his last letter, it says, 'This will be my last message for a long time, perhaps forever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have been quite happy in these last few days, since hearing that Irma--' which is our mother-- 'is still alive, but now I must go the way of my fate.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I may-- it may well be that the way will reunite me with my beloved darling,' which means his wife, who died. 'If you can, please tell my family that I would dearly have loved to see them again.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But frankly, I do not know how.' This was the last communication.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I now know that he was one victim of a mass execution.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was, at that time, the method of extermination, when they had to dig their own graves and strip and were mowed down with machine guns.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Around-- no, I was deported on April 1st, '42.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means before that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
